&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A minimum of 10+ years of professional project management or relevant experience, which includes at least 2 years experience project managing in the following areas 1) managing SAAS software projects, 2) participating in and/or driving implementations, and 3) working in a client facing project

